<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Chubb cautions shareholders, talks underway.</title>
<headline>Chubb cautions shareholders, talks underway.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-03-14</dateline>
<text>
<p>Investment holding group Chubb Holdings Ltd said on Friday shareholders should exercise caution in share dealings  until further notice on the acquisition offer for British parent Chubb Security plc. -- Johannesburg newroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
